text: Horgau () is a municipality in the district of Augsburg in Bavaria in Germany. Districts (villages) of the municipality Horgau: Horgau, Horgauergreut, Auerbach, Bieselbach, Horgau Bahnhof, Lindgraben, Schäfstoß, Herpfenried ==References== == Other websites == * Category:Augsburg (district)
